on the Video on Demand section 


1:06:08.147 --> 1:06:11.017
of JW Broadcasting later this month. 


1:06:11.017 --> 1:06:15.989
In fact, Part 2 is a video entitled
The Inside Story.


1:06:15.988 --> 1:06:19.491
It is scheduled to be posted
next Monday, December 11.


